---
import ContactHeroImage from '../assets/news-placeholder-contact.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/NewsPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Contact Delfi"
	description="How to reach the Delfi newsroom, send tips, and get support during crisis coverage"
	pubDate={new Date('2026-03-21T17:56:18.411Z')}
	updatedDate={new Date('2026-03-22T17:56:18.411Z')}
	heroImage={ContactHeroImage}
	heroImageAlt="Delfi newsroom"
>
	<h2>Need to contact us?</h2>
	<p>
		This is the emergency version of Delfi. The portal is lightweight and static for reliability, but
		our newsroom and reader support channels continue to work as usual.
	</p>
	<p>
		News and public information are updated 24/7 during active incidents. Use the contacts below for
		news tips, corrections, and media requests.
	</p>

	<h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
	<h3>How do I send a news tip?</h3>
	<p>
		Email tips@delfi.ee with what happened, where, and when. If possible, include photos or video and
		a callback number. Urgent safety-related tips are prioritized.
	</p>
	<h3>How do I report an error in an article?</h3>
	<p>
		Send corrections to corrections@delfi.ee with the article link and a short explanation. The
		editorial team reviews all correction requests.
	</p>
	<h3>Is coverage monitored around the clock?</h3>
	<p>
		Yes. During crisis periods, Delfi publishes verified updates 24/7 and prioritizes high-impact
		public information.
	</p>

	<h2>Official Contacts</h2>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>News tips:</strong> tips@delfi.ee</li>
		<li><strong>Corrections:</strong> corrections@delfi.ee</li>
		<li><strong>Reader support:</strong> support@delfi.ee</li>
		<li><strong>Press and media:</strong> press@delfi.ee</li>
		<li><strong>Partnerships:</strong> partner@delfi.ee</li>
		<li><strong>Phone:</strong> +372 1234 5678 (24/7)</li>
	</ul>
	<p>
		If email delivery is delayed, call the newsroom line and leave your name, topic, and callback
		number.
	</p>
</Layout>
